summary:
Laser cutting cells - 
Laser cutting a photo I had taken through the microscope eyepiece of cells within the nervous system. I...
body:
Laser cutting cells -

Laser cutting a photo I had taken through the microscope eyepiece of cells within the nervous system. I won’t be taking this technique further as it doesn’t reflect the 3D structures of the cells. It would also be to fragile to work with in assesmbling a larger sculpture.
